:name: RISCV32-Virtual
:description: This script is prepared to run Zephyr on a Renode RISCV32 board.

$name?="RISCV32-Virtual"

using sysbus
mach create $name
machine LoadPlatformDescription $ORIGIN/riscv32_virtual.repl

showAnalyzer uart0
cpu PerformanceInMips 4

macro reset
"""
    sysbus LoadELF $bin
"""
runMacro $reset
